# =============================================================================
# .dockerignore
#
# Goal: keep the Hugging Face Space image as small as possible so judges can
# pull and run it locally quickly. The Dockerfile does `COPY . .`, so
# everything in this file is excluded from the build context.
#
# In particular, we exclude:
#   - GRPO trained model weights (multi-GB; reviewers don't need them to test
#     the environment / UI / OpenEnv server).
#   - The training notebook + its outputs (the Space serves the env, not training).
#   - Local eval result JSONs (regenerable; bulky).
#   - Caches, virtualenvs, build artifacts, OS junk.
# =============================================================================

# Trained model weights (intentionally NOT shipped — keep Space lean)
oversight-arena-trained/
oversight-arena-grpo/
training/oversight-arena-trained/
training/oversight-arena-grpo/
**/checkpoint-*/
**/*.safetensors
**/pytorch_model.bin

# Training notebook + its run-time outputs
training/.ipynb_checkpoints/
training/training_log_snapshot.json
training/grpo_episodes_*.jsonl
training/grpo_training.log
training/eval/results/
training/plots/
training/oversight-arena-grpo/
training_log_snapshot.json
grpo_episodes_*.jsonl
reward_curves.png

# Eval result JSONs are regenerable and not needed to run the Space
eval/results/*.json

# Python caches
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

# Secrets / env files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Logs
*.log
*.out
*.err
logs/

# Notebook checkpoints anywhere
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Build / packaging
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# OS / editor metadata
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
.git/
.gitignore
docs/
